msgstr "1. On the Devices page, run \"Scan for devices\" (or skip the scan and adopt by address directly). 2. Press Adopt on a discovered row, or \"Adopt device\" in the header. 3. Give the device a stable identifier and name, check the driver and management address, and optionally set a desired mode and an offline-alarm severity. 4. Confirm. The device is created in ADOPTING and its supervised driver immediately probes it toward ONLINE."

