#: src/pages/docs/ConfigPage.tsx:125
msgid "A CSS-grid layout with <0>columns</0> and <1>rows</1> track lists (<2>fr</2> / <3>px</3> / <4>%</4>), a <5>gap</5>, and an <6>areas</6> map that names where each cell sits."
